construction program in 30 points throughout the country and has
over 8,950 stands at different stages of construction," Socks
said.
</P>
<P>
He said the trust was seeking external funding to finance the
surveying and servicing of stands and construction of the houses.
</P>
<P>
"The five-year plan should see a minimum of 1,200 houses
constructed each year with a total of 6,000 houses completed in
five years," he added.
</P>
<P>
The houses will vary from medium, low cost and ultra low cost
with the majority falling within the low cost category, he said.
