conflict to fully commit themselves to a peaceful solution, to
put the unity and cohesion of their country beyond any other
consideration and to seize the opportunity offered to them by the
international mediation."
</P>
<P>
Salim also urged them to scrupulously observe the cease-fire
pact so as to spare the people of Brazzaville further suffering
and devastation and put an end to the ordeal they have been
experienced during the past weeks. 
