<HEADLINE> Zambian President to Visit Mauritius, Rwanda, </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, July 16 (Xinhua) -- Zambian President Frederick
Chiluba will pay a state visit to Mauritius, Rwanda and Tanzania
next week, a state house spokesman announced here today.
</P>
