the president "is the only person who can save the situation".
</P>
<P>
Mabvuku mp Pamela Tungamirai said if the president continued
to ignore the war veterans, he might destroy the unquestionable
loyalty, faith and confidence which most ex-combatants had for
the ruling Zanu (PF) leadership. 
