<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 16 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai will focus on supporting
54 big enterprise groups to back up its overall economy, according
to a municipal working conference on enterprise groups.
</P>
<P>
"Shanghai needs big enterprise groups to facilitate its
ambition of building itself into a global economic, financial and
trade center," said a municipal official at the conference.
</P>
<P>
