<HEADLINE> Clinton Congratulates New Irish PM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 15 (Xinhua) -- U.S. President Bill Clinton
today called new Irish Prime Minister Bertie Ahern and expressed
his hope to establish "personal one-on-one contact" to help
achieve peace in Northern Ireland.
</P>
